  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Breaker Brass is an ogryn slave-labourer in the House of Chains, forging war machines for his House Goliath masters and crushing their enemies with steel fists. When civil war tears through the factorum, a rival gang spends him like scrap and leaves him broken. He rises instead with golden fists, new intelligence and a purpose that can become a servitor revolt. A brutal but strangely hopeful Necromunda novella about a discarded worker discovering the shape of freedom in the machinery built to own him.",
